PN,30201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780876973
OL,3,CAverage pocket money received by
OL,4,Cchildren revealed by money app
OL,6,FChildren have received a 12p-a-week
OL,7,Fpocket money pay rise in 2026 so far,
OL,8,Fcompared with what they were getting a
OL,9,Fyear earlier, figures from a money app
OL,10,Findicate.
OL,12,FYoungsters aged seven to 18 received
OL,13,F#9.90 on average per week between
OL,14,FJanuary and April 2026, marking a 1.2%
OL,15,Fincrease compared with #9.78 between
OL,16,FJanuary and April 2025, according to
OL,17,Fanonymised data from GoHenry.
OL,19,FThere is also a 3p-per-week gender
OL,20,Fgap, with girls receiving #9.89 per
OL,21,Fweek this year and boys getting #9.91.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780876973
OL,3,CAverage pocket money received by
OL,4,Cchildren revealed by money app
OL,6,FThe annual percentage pocket money
OL,7,Fincrease for children is less than
OL,8,Fhalf the rate of the consumer prices
OL,9,Findex (CPI) rate of inflation in
OL,10,FApril, which was 2.8%, according to
OL,11,FOffice for National Statistics' (ONS)
OL,12,Ffigures.
OL,14,FThis perhaps indicates that parents
OL,15,Fhave been feeling the pinch from
OL,16,Frising living costs.
OL,18,FGoHenry also found that children in
OL,19,Fthe south east of England are
OL,20,Freceiving the highest weekly pocket
OL,21,Fmoney, at #12.88.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
