OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780876973
OL,3,CAverage pocket money received by
OL,4,Cchildren revealed by money app
OL,6,FChildren in the east of England
OL,7,Freceive the lowest average, at #8.57,
OL,8,Faccording to figures from the app.
OL,10,FLooking at payments for chores,
OL,11,Ftidying bedrooms is the most common
OL,12,Ftask to generate account top-ups, with
OL,13,Fan average pocket money payment of
OL,14,F#1.14 for doing this.
OL,16,FMusic practice is the highest-earning
OL,17,Fchore at an average pocket money
OL,18,Fpayment of #1.84.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
