OL,3,CAverage pocket money received by
OL,4,Cchildren revealed by money app
OL,6,FHolidays are the most popular savings
OL,7,Fgoal for children's pots, followed by
OL,8,Fbirthdays and electronics, GoHenry
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FGrocery shops and supermarkets are the
OL,12,Ftop place for children to spend money,
OL,13,Ffollowed by restaurants, clothing
OL,14,Fshops, transport and health and beauty
OL,15,Fshops, according to the data.
OL,17,FLouise Hill, founder of GoHenry said:
OL,18,F"This mid-year snapshot shows
OL,19,Fsomething really important.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
