OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780876973
OL,3,CAverage pocket money received by
OL,4,Cchildren revealed by money app
OL,6,F"Despite the rising cost of living,
OL,7,Fkids are still setting money aside
OL,8,Fweek after week, saving an average of
OL,9,F#3.93 per week, and it's become second
OL,10,Fnature for them.
OL,12,F"It's exciting to watch their world
OL,13,Fgrow alongside their financial
OL,14,Findependence.
OL,16,F"We're seeing kids make more
OL,17,Findependent choices about where they
OL,18,Fspend, from supermarkets to transport
OL,19,Fand health and beauty, reflecting
OL,20,Ftheir growing autonomy and confidence
OL,21,Fwhen it comes to managing their money."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU}D@gO]
