OL,6,FThe analysis was based on a sample of
OL,7,Fmore than 600,000 children saving with
OL,8,FGoHenry aged between seven and 18,
OL,9,Fcomparing January 1 2025 to April 15
OL,10,F2025 with January 1 2026 to April 15
OL,11,F2026.
OL,13,FHere are average weekly pocket money
OL,14,Fpayments by the age of the child
OL,15,Fbetween January and April 2026,
OL,16,Faccording to GoHenry:
OL,18,FSeven: #4.30
OL,20,FEight: #4.44
